{"title":"Resistencia bacteriana","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/Infectología/Resistencia bacteriana-2024.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"Resistencia bacteriana\\NBacilos G(-), Cocos G(+), Anaerobios","guid":"ST0auWzbJa0VxTOe_tP9Rw","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"Introd.","guid":"74LrlKbsUioeFqmSOWAVgQ","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"- Resist. Antimicrobiana (RA): Fenómeno progresivo, acumulativo, multiresistente.","guid":"pfbItWEqTHk9KcBGMAd4fA","children":[]},{"id":"3","parent":"1","text":"- Detección: Hospitales + Comunidad.","guid":"0bgOgTPwr82gTbtgnUUEIw","children":[]},{"id":"4","parent":"1","text":"General","guid":"nLHVywOLupLw2_2I1uP_HA","children":[{"id":"5","parent":"4","text":"- Mutaciones reguladoras → síntesis desregulada → cepas hiperproductoras.","guid":"PFXvuThRvj4GXxMZEZpPtg","children":[]},{"id":"6","parent":"4","text":"- Impacto hospitalario: necesidad de carbapenems ante resistencia avanzada.","guid":"QROutQw9Sy84qbccKgj67Q","children":[]},{"id":"7","parent":"4","text":"- **Mecanismo de\\NResistencia:**","guid":"YhHVdGq9NcBns5DiGlENyg","children":[{"id":"8","parent":"7","text":"- Enzimáticos: Degrada antibióticos → G(-)","guid":"Ik4S_1ha_CVTRR_6CaqFCQ","children":[]},{"id":"9","parent":"7","text":"- Estructurales: Cambios en pared celular/sitios blanco → G(+)","guid":"L18hDHSsB7IuwbzHYg4dPw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"10","parent":"1","text":"Ejemplos","guid":"qHhrYQi6_2_Wh4171u9VHg","children":[{"id":"11","parent":"10","text":"- Comunidad:","guid":"6fcSFNHbRg52Mb0JdPB5EA","children":[{"id":"12","parent":"11","text":"1. Gonococo -> Resist. Penicilina","guid":"OC0u5D-IFntWpdGYBhjADg","children":[]},{"id":"13","parent":"11","text":"2. S. Typhi -> Multiresist.","guid":"qd4SMUczd-h7ZezC4dFIcw","children":[]},{"id":"14","parent":"11","text":"3. M. tuberculosis -> Multiresist.","guid":"bbr-DHqXDaocZqDmvaaXNw","children":[]},{"id":"15","parent":"11","text":"4. Shigella sp -> Multiresist.","guid":"xEo9Vzrm-WnSw8y6Dn-ybw","children":[]},{"id":"16","parent":"11","text":"5. E. coli (ITU) -> Resist. Ampicilina, Cotrimoxazol","guid":"dqPnpw2WQI7F5nuNrSIdAQ","children":[]},{"id":"17","parent":"11","text":"6. Neumococo -> Resist. Penicilina, Cefalosporinas","guid":"XCYiV-NesE776CrA5rFgJQ","children":[]},{"id":"18","parent":"11","text":"7. H. influenzae -> Resist. Ampicilina","guid":"uMsJDYNGybQK06RjEr30eQ","children":[]},{"id":"19","parent":"11","text":"8. M. catharralis -> Resist. Ampicilina","guid":"Fxmd8NxrsqB_Ezxa-KyfKA","children":[]},{"id":"20","parent":"11","text":"9. S. aureus -> Resist. Penicilina","guid":"pgH4_KPPsuLIplTh1k8W_A","children":[]},{"id":"21","parent":"11","text":"10. Plasmodium sp -> Resist. Antimaláricos","guid":"nIk3n5ycWR0BcHY6uC0YGg","children":[]}]},{"id":"22","parent":"10","text":"- Hospitales:","guid":"xE4eYY1A3uSp0RvpLaElkQ","children":[{"id":"23","parent":"22","text":"1. Staphylococci -> Resist. Cloxacilina, Multiresist.","guid":"Iqtfq0C7Q9YCe0Hm4csx6Q","children":[]},{"id":"24","parent":"22","text":"2. Enterococo -> Resist. Beta-lactámicos, Aminoglucósidos, Vancomicina","guid":"js4tvqgdX-_c4zck_HqJ4w","children":[]},{"id":"25","parent":"22","text":"3. Bacilos G(-) -> Resist. Beta-lactámicos, Aminoglucósidos, Quinolonas, etc.","guid":"DfUkC9xP-wKJ93yTsMjs0A","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"26","parent":"1","text":"Desarrollo RA","guid":"vbjKivuCiMNZwoPgF-_-SQ","children":[{"id":"27","parent":"26","text":"- Frecuencia baja pre-exposición (10^-6 a 10^-7).","guid":"B1LMYswondr8znk9hNXJNg","children":[]},{"id":"28","parent":"26","text":"- Selección post-exposición ->\\NReemplazo por población resistente.","guid":"_-IjdeBs-USIKosmebz46g","children":[{"id":"29","parent":"28","text":"- Menor virulencia y replicación resistente.","guid":"R4mutEv3QvKU0yUJ2vxZgw","children":[]},{"id":"30","parent":"28","text":"- Recolonización nativa si cesa presión selectiva.","guid":"F1HZ2-yb0bQAU3VQhTshHA","children":[]},{"id":"31","parent":"28","text":"- RA común en hospitales (presión selectiva constante).","guid":"SESf_oq7ehnl6FxDUuyUPw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"32","parent":"1","text":"Factores de\\NDiseminación","guid":"SDg0alFrFYCgmcYL1Seoaw","children":[{"id":"33","parent":"32","text":"- Uso irracional de antibióticos: Comunitario y Nosocomial.","guid":"G9XUW1ca_cuvqEt9lXFsSw","children":[]},{"id":"34","parent":"32","text":"- Prácticas humanas y presión selectiva comunitaria.","guid":"y2sc-9mn9yBT6HlDbx6xRw","children":[]},{"id":"35","parent":"32","text":"- Uso en industria pecuaria -> Transferencia de resistencia.","guid":"D5MRBxRnUO0RsKcbuEz7Sw","children":[]}]},{"id":"36","parent":"1","text":"Factores Culturales y\\NMédicos (Uso Irracional)","guid":"oeCw0cR2WXqNSNhNWQrzIg","children":[{"id":"37","parent":"36","text":"- Prescripción como sedante.","guid":"NO2DvKYmLGxaaRMDkrDU1g","children":[]},{"id":"38","parent":"36","text":"- Antibióticos para conveniencia médica.","guid":"1tZ8wOS3cK-MncwHW3s8DQ","children":[]},{"id":"39","parent":"36","text":"- Uso en infecciones virales, diarrea aguda, odinofagia.","guid":"Mq78MxKDYHIgFnusPZ-CTQ","children":[]},{"id":"40","parent":"36","text":"- Profilaxis quirúrgica indiscriminada.","guid":"ESEl2Hz5o01h8VULN9BDMg","children":[]},{"id":"41","parent":"36","text":"- Presión parental y farmacéutica.","guid":"JA-YuSOMy31RnYUjd32BqA","children":[]},{"id":"42","parent":"36","text":"- Regulación insuficiente en venta de antimicrobianos.","guid":"EMbUhhG6AZQ97DCZXWbgvw","children":[]},{"id":"43","parent":"36","text":"- Uso en ganadería para mejora de producción.","guid":"KqXY4Dl8VD8ozImdOl75Gw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"44","parent":"0","text":"**Bacilos Gram\\NNegativos (G(-))**","guid":"By9oJE7YOHMfrZ-NGFCN_A","children":[{"id":"45","parent":"44","text":"General","guid":"FOGRU1Zm9gpu5xJuYLNtEw","children":[{"id":"46","parent":"45","text":"- **Enfoque en:**","guid":"YMY57jfz168zJD9VFD6R1A","children":[{"id":"47","parent":"46","text":"- Beta-lactámicos","guid":"XT7-akZ9tLByXMKZPAZ5ZQ","children":[]},{"id":"48","parent":"46","text":"- Aminoglucósidos","guid":"AqOzqQrZ7HpU7o9jbfK3uQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"49","parent":"45","text":"- **Mecanismo de Resistencia:**","guid":"V8sIhlxkhAR7j87IfRcgtw","children":[{"id":"50","parent":"49","text":"- Predominantemente enzimático.","guid":"Nx-YnxLXauBRwln1Boa07A","children":[]}]},{"id":"51","parent":"45","text":"- **Proceso:**","guid":"WODDvwh7sHNdHTlebcJVEg","children":[{"id":"52","parent":"51","text":"- Enzimas descomponen antibióticos, impidiendo su acción.","guid":"XuKmfUwES81OdcImNuiRIA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"53","parent":"44","text":"Mecanismos","guid":"YB3E50SJE0NfK5aHVflRpA","children":[{"id":"54","parent":"53","text":"1. **Modificación\\NEnzimática del Antibiótico**","guid":"Vv57Y2c-ey4AEPssND15zQ","children":[{"id":"55","parent":"54","text":"Beta-lactamasas","guid":"UcsHamAzW8ATMxseQ4cycA","children":[{"id":"56","parent":"55","text":"- **Grupos Principales:** A-D","guid":"PJCXuE7a-xIyiwe2XiBWRg","children":[]},{"id":"57","parent":"55","text":"- Enfoque en Grupos A y C, prevalentes en G(-) comunitarios y nosocomiales.","guid":"KNV2R3ahj8IhRxtuHLJbhQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"58","parent":"54","text":"- Enzimas modificantes de aminoglucósidos","guid":"fUeqQEUygpYeUptBVRKyxg","children":[]},{"id":"59","parent":"54","text":"- Cloranfenicol acetil-transferasa","guid":"IZcGmhniaglSKdN9WLafOQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"60","parent":"53","text":"2. **Cambios en Permeabilidad**","guid":"IY--jln6ezVEFogMQybFKA","children":[{"id":"61","parent":"60","text":"- Mutación en porina D2 (P. aeruginosa) → resistencia a carbapenems","guid":"LLnU6SPsLXNfPVQlBZqYqQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"62","parent":"53","text":"3. **Modificaciones en\\NSitio de Ataque**","guid":"c9zlPhZAW4kb3WRhIJa6KA","children":[{"id":"63","parent":"62","text":"- Cambio de afinidad en PBP → afecta penicilina","guid":"LGfd5jxajYRzXO27C0qEYw","children":[]},{"id":"64","parent":"62","text":"- Mutaciones en DNA girasa → resistencia a quinolonas","guid":"CF7ZUUHSr-FCMxWEE2sIuw","children":[]},{"id":"65","parent":"62","text":"- Modificaciones ribosomales → resistencia a aminoglucósidos","guid":"YN1TlXZNUV1_PXITN9vO-A","children":[]},{"id":"66","parent":"62","text":"- Modificaciones ribosomales cruzadas (MLS) → resistencia a macrólidos, lincosamidas, estreptogramina","guid":"XYvMjH9ObUBsGUjFC0f8aw","children":[]},{"id":"67","parent":"62","text":"- Reemplazo de D-alanina por D-lactato en péptidoglucano → resistencia a vancomicina","guid":"cbwrBlxdO_g7p9_zbwPVRg","children":[]}]},{"id":"68","parent":"53","text":"4. **Mecanismos de Eflujo**","guid":"N3VGChmOQIxx3utGP9QfWw","children":[{"id":"69","parent":"68","text":"- Bombas de eflujo para tetraciclina, cloranfenicol, quinolonas, beta-lactámicos, eritromicina, etc.","guid":"OiyI_HsauIYmMVLRZpRm4g","children":[]}]},{"id":"70","parent":"53","text":"5. **Transporte Inefectivo**","guid":"Kl9SJ1J8mip0GhL7B-sesw","children":[{"id":"71","parent":"70","text":"- Deficiente captación de aminoglucósidos en anaerobios","guid":"W2DwbjQSAMpTPygWPD5EAw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"72","parent":"44","text":"Grupo A: Betalactamasas de serina","guid":"Z_Ulu33Jw1JXjiAKZt413w","children":[{"id":"73","parent":"72","text":"General","guid":"Xct9rw6Ady4raIxCNWDY8g","children":[{"id":"74","parent":"73","text":"- Mecanismo: Rompen anillo betalactámico","guid":"W4mkFMipKdVEZt3i32g0Lg","children":[]},{"id":"75","parent":"73","text":"- Sensibles a inhibidores de betalactamasas (p. ej., ácido clavulánico)","guid":"WGwv1n03I1R9xRNjkoG3sw","children":[]}]},{"id":"76","parent":"72","text":"Comunitario","guid":"","children":[{"id":"77","parent":"76","text":"Penicilinasas","guid":"JxeR91hjoZ9JD_55E8gEnQ","children":[{"id":"78","parent":"77","text":"- Asociadas a: E. coli, Klebsiella pneumoniae, H. influenzae, Neisseria gonorrhoeae.","guid":"Za8xkDfRRLwd4E4NQORtIQ","children":[]},{"id":"79","parent":"77","text":"- Genes: Mayormente plasmidiales (excepto en K. pneumoniae).","guid":"RyzS-UlRXf1HuzREC__d2g","children":[]},{"id":"80","parent":"77","text":"- Evolución: Enzimas TEM-1, TEM-2 y SHV predominantes en cepas comunitarias.","guid":"RZFsSwAS6Xs9GbDtNii2-Q","children":[]},{"id":"81","parent":"77","text":"- Mecanismo: Mutaciones en sitio activo → cambio cualitativo en la actividad enzimática.","guid":"esu1ZztHNa0Sh7CPavkLZg","children":[]},{"id":"82","parent":"77","text":"- Resistencia: A ampicilina-amoxicilina, cefalosporinas de 1ª generación.","guid":"Ydx1RjGPmH1gQi7MVeEFJg","children":[]},{"id":"83","parent":"77","text":"- Tratamiento: Cefalosporinas de 2ª/3ª generación o amoxicilina + inhibidores de beta-lactamasas efectivos.","guid":"HH_l4jwAQnwnkWplcrTZhg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"84","parent":"72","text":"Hospitalario","guid":"","children":[{"id":"85","parent":"84","text":"Cefalosporinasas","guid":"JFPag1QJ0bolOwwGKW4kZg","children":[{"id":"86","parent":"85","text":"Asociados a: E. coli y K. pneumoniae","guid":"fYMLeyVWsw4CfHVhJJqdcg","children":[]},{"id":"87","parent":"85","text":"- Origen: Presión selectiva en hospitales → evolución hacia BLEE.","guid":"THgMjWUh2Sc9Pwd8cA9CxA","children":[]},{"id":"88","parent":"85","text":"- Características: Mayor espectro, mutaciones en sitio activo.","guid":"cj2FMU3rTC17m562fSL0jQ","children":[]},{"id":"89","parent":"85","text":"- Resistencia: A cefalosporinas de 3ª generación (ej. ceftazidima).","guid":"NiWw6W4GMIdtt5V6VjFaYA","children":[]},{"id":"90","parent":"85","text":"- Implicación: Conduce al uso de carbapenems en hospitales.","guid":"dASP4GrwTWVbvhOwUbBlPg","children":[]},{"id":"91","parent":"85","text":"- Problema: Alto costo, limitadas alternativas terapéuticas.","guid":"VjTzo2eW87plikGlHfdrKw","children":[]}]},{"id":"92","parent":"84","text":"Carbapenemasas","guid":"AbwhXhO4qYZJV-ndZEXiiA","children":[{"id":"93","parent":"92","text":"- **Frecuencia:** Infrecuentes en ambientes hospitalarios.","guid":"wPcRaC6N9JoLNy6_3nJ0-g","children":[]},{"id":"94","parent":"92","text":"- **Capacidad:** Degradan todos los beta-lactámicos, incluyendo carbapenémicos.","guid":"uNO2wvqLvo-mZzQkYFllig","children":[]},{"id":"95","parent":"92","text":"- **Inhibición:** No son inhibidas por sulbactam, tazobactam, ni ácido clavulánico.","guid":"CNy1_R8QES0-5wVeVOcJyw","children":[]},{"id":"96","parent":"92","text":"- **Excepción:** Aztreonam mantiene actividad contra cepas con carbapenemasas.","guid":"RnKKIwLCwsgq6qMVcGxgUg","children":[]},{"id":"97","parent":"92","text":"- **Presencia Habitual:** Stenotrophomonas maltophilia (cromosómica, constitutiva).","guid":"d74fZyQrIvUjAd3ne4g_jQ","children":[{"id":"98","parent":"97","text":"KPC","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"99","parent":"92","text":"- **Detección en Otras Especies:** Ocasional en plasmidios de P. aeruginosa, S. marcescens, K. pneumoniae.","guid":"Rdvj_iP04pQhx6MdN0WrIg","children":[]},{"id":"100","parent":"92","text":"- **Detección Fenotípica:** Mediante adición de EDTA en cultivo, que quelata zinc, necesario para su actividad.","guid":"ZssUFSHRuwMX-AIVCx7umQ","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"101","parent":"44","text":"Grupo B: Metalobetalactamasas (MBLs)","guid":"jvVnqBDseffFGlBGowkcdg","children":[{"id":"102","parent":"101","text":"General ","guid":"wZgJFhPRLYvNLTnbuLwVkg","children":[{"id":"103","parent":"102","text":"- Requieren Zn²⁺ u otros metales para actividad","guid":"4GxP33rlE-4K5HLD3MCd9A","children":[]},{"id":"104","parent":"102","text":"- Hidrolizan: Penicilinas, Cefalosporinas, Carbapenems","guid":"Mu9KB-VqJYj3G8QbQubk3Q","children":[]},{"id":"105","parent":"102","text":"- Resistentes a inhibidores de betalactamasas","guid":"FvNPMBTS99ofxZ9HaBAnKg","children":[]}]},{"id":"106","parent":"101","text":"NDM-1\\N(New Delhi metalo-beta-lactamase-1)","guid":"M_JoW4wSQhemCMkzW0HLEQ","children":[{"id":"107","parent":"106","text":"- **Origen**: Detectada inicialmente en cepas de Klebsiella pneumoniae y Escherichia coli.","guid":"nvkLMmpcN-GgKMHgD3Nv3Q","children":[]},{"id":"108","parent":"106","text":"- **Actividad**: Hidroliza casi todos los betalactámicos.","guid":"vBXnC0WOsZfJxm6Ju8OFoQ","children":[]},{"id":"109","parent":"106","text":"- **Resistencia**: No es inhibida por inhibidores convencionales de betalactamasas como ácido clavulánico, sulbactam o tazobactam.","guid":"fQ4gHtwmbuGfroeUlndlzg","children":[]}]},{"id":"110","parent":"101","text":"VIM","guid":"_K0SaFnJTuVlav4zjvmGcw","children":[]},{"id":"111","parent":"101","text":"OXA","guid":"jsAQKWlAhuVGvxOhs41CZA","children":[]}]},{"id":"112","parent":"44","text":"Grupo C","guid":"TjeePhVWbAwKBYwrS0BHSQ","children":[{"id":"113","parent":"112","text":"- **Inducción:** Normalmente inducibles, aumentan síntesis de enzimas.","guid":"DOHrSz0kf889SRWtRw50SA","children":[]},{"id":"114","parent":"112","text":"- **Capacidad:** Hidrolizan beta-lactámicos (ampicilina, amoxicilina, cefalosporinas).","guid":"OD84VmN6aH4totsqb7R-YA","children":[]},{"id":"115","parent":"112","text":"- **Resistencia:** Incluso a cefalosporinas de todas generaciones; susceptible solo a carbapenems.","guid":"U5PHOgLHxdIUp918ffMZYg","children":[]},{"id":"116","parent":"112","text":"- Sensibilidad: Parcial a inhibidores como sulbactam, tazobactam, ácido clavulánico.","guid":"flEQZh8wo4k9adbRV-1OQg","children":[]},{"id":"117","parent":"112","text":"- Factores limitantes\\Nde inhibición:","guid":"GGTl2zCiMRwsVUGFTOBd2w","children":[{"id":"118","parent":"117","text":"- Menor permeabilidad membranal.","guid":"NmI79mu2QC5G7UImPDUwTA","children":[]},{"id":"119","parent":"117","text":"- Mayor producción enzimática.","guid":"aDDvxHci3Wsj5JnnFjs32A","children":[]},{"id":"120","parent":"117","text":"- Tipo de enzima (ej. SHV difíciles de inhibir).","guid":"B5qnfGF1CKlgxWXOVBK0CQ","children":[]},{"id":"121","parent":"117","text":"- Aumento en costo de tratamiento.","guid":"a--5dz-9lYM191uPIhVqYA","children":[]},{"id":"122","parent":"117","text":"- Necesidad de usar combinaciones de cefalosporinas con inhibidores o carbapenems.","guid":"LcPGCyOu8Ql4RsTBLBTWcQ","children":[]},{"id":"123","parent":"117","text":"- Decisión basada en resistencia y opciones disponibles.","guid":"Qt-UkjWwm5IEAiSzW0R6bg","children":[]}]},{"id":"124","parent":"112","text":"- **Especies asociadas:** P. aeruginosa, Enterobacter sp, Citrobacter freundii, Serratia sp.","guid":"VURf_AjB8HcF3jgVJw9nZg","children":[]}]},{"id":"125","parent":"44","text":"- **Resistencia a Ceftazidima y Mecanismos de\\NResistencia a Beta-lactámicos:**","guid":"b0iPzmF9qQJT_7nURIi1FA","children":[{"id":"126","parent":"125","text":"- Resistencia a ceftazidima en\\Nantibiograma señala:","guid":"GUOhGgYESi5dryRTBTNakg","children":[{"id":"127","parent":"126","text":"- Hiperproducción de AmpC o","guid":"RcHfsROmf-InSMTyc4WlvA","children":[]},{"id":"128","parent":"126","text":"- Presencia de BLEE.","guid":"N1Vw7B-PibMfmnwtejUFfg","children":[]}]},{"id":"129","parent":"125","text":"- Susceptibilidad a\\Nceftazidima indica:","guid":"U_QHGH2eWDZYR_qYcAGtfg","children":[{"id":"130","parent":"129","text":"- Ausencia de hiperproducción AmpC.","guid":"bLBypjEyM4h0QEOpUuVqgQ","children":[]},{"id":"131","parent":"129","text":"- Beta-lactamasas plasmidiales no son de espectro extendido.","guid":"LgEGYA66EatAtQnYDETh4g","children":[]},{"id":"132","parent":"129","text":"- Identificación precisa del mecanismo de resistencia orienta el tratamiento adecuado.","guid":"CflFfAKXXTgxH580Izzmlg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"133","parent":"44","text":"Bacilos no\\Nfermentados","guid":"SblMbFJdvtso7WilIh2JLA","children":[{"id":"134","parent":"133","text":"- **Resistencia a Carbapenémicos en P.\\Naeruginosa y Stenotrophomona maltophilia**","guid":"WGQ8wATKBEES27O4ChE0BA","children":[{"id":"135","parent":"134","text":"- **Mecanismos de\\NResistencia**","guid":"dduMvT0zDhs0jRL_c16YOQ","children":[{"id":"136","parent":"135","text":"- P. aeruginosa:","guid":"YonBKTcJiGAX-TWrYEQV1w","children":[{"id":"137","parent":"136","text":"- Mutaciones en porinas.","guid":"ApX8OlBb17tnlD-sC3KyNw","chi